lass=\"css-1gomreu\"><a class=\"UserLink-link\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/gopro-90\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-za-detail-view-element_name=\"User\">知乎用户Wm7C8w</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AuthorInfo-detail\">\n<div class=\"AuthorInfo-badge\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"LabelContainer-wrapper\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"Voters\"><button class=\"Button Button--plain\" type=\"button\">13 人赞同了该文章</button></span></div>\n</header>\n<div class=\"Post-RichTextContainer\">\n<div class=\"css-1yuhvjn\">\n<div class=\"RichText ztext Post-RichText css-4em6pe\">\n<p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"fehz8nsI\"><strong>1：首先在手机上安装GoPro应用，手机wifi和蓝牙全部打开，然后相机上操作屏幕下滑，首选项--连接--无线连接（开）-连接应用。</strong></p>\n<p data-pid=\"vSmeeUbZ\"><strong>2：在手机上打开app，点击连接摄像机，会出现蓝牙配对请求，点击配对，会自动连接。</strong></p>\n<p data-pid=\"roXQ51MF\"><strong>3：更改摄像机名称的界面，可忽略，也可以改成自己喜欢的名字（需英文字母）或保留摄像机本身的名称。</strong></p>\n<p data-pid=\"XbFPL4mT\"><strong>4：点击我们开始吧，会有提示是否连接wifi，请点击加入完成连接。</strong></p>\n<p data-pid=\"FHRdgo-z\"><strong>5：安卓手机建议关闭智能wifi功能，这个功能会切断手机app与相机的连接。</strong></p>\n<p data-pid=\"iV3yoZD4\"><strong>6：安装app时所有出现的提示均要点击是，切记不要点击否，会有影响app与手机的连接步成功。</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ContentItem-time\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\">发布于 2020-01-04 20:17</div>\n<div class=\"Post-topicsAndReviewer\">\n<div class=\"TopicList Post-Topics\">\n<div class=\"Tag Topic css-1s3a4zw\" data-za-detail-view-path-module=\"TopicItem\" data-za-extra-module=\"{&quot;card&quot;:{&quot;content&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Topic&quot;,&quot;token&quot;:&quot;19676891&quot;}}}\">\n<div class=\"css-1gomreu\">GoPro</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"Tag Topic css-1s3a4zw\" data-za-detail-view-path-module=\"TopicItem\" data-za-extra-module=\"{&quot;card&quot;:{&quot;content&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Topic&quot;,&quot;token&quot;:&quot;20050454&quot;}}}\">\n<div class=\"css-1gomreu\">运动相机</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"Ta